If I use the actual q.js filename at a line number BEFORE `qStartingLine`, the frame should NOT be filtered in either version (since `lineNumber < qStartingLine`). If I use it at a line number WITHIN `[qStartingLine, qEndingLine]`, it should be filtered in BOTH versions.

